      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, appearing as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its deep factory luster with no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings; it has been kept under a breathable car cover in a climate-controlled garage and recently treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple with absolutely no bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It features a comprehensive, documented service history with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule at certified dealerships. The engine bay is immaculate, showing no signs of fluid seepage or road grime, and the undercarriage is equally clean. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a peak-condition vehicle that has been pampered since day one. All original keys, manuals, and service records are included.",
